              a.articles__slider-link(href="#") Read More
          li.articles__slider-item
            .articles__slider-img-block
              img.articles__slider-img(src="./images/blog/article-2.png" alt="#")
            .articles__slider-title-block
              h3.articles__slider-title Skyrocketing in The Designing Career, Why Not?
              p.articles__slider-desc Ever thought of jumping into the world of design as a career? If not, you may want to look at what the word ‘design’ actually means. Design is a method of designing aesthetic actions that are carried out.
            .articles__slider-link-block
              a.articles__slider-link(href="#") Read More
          li.articles__slider-item
            .articles__slider-img-block
              img.articles__slider-img(src="./images/blog/article-3.png" alt="#")
            .articles__slider-title-block
              h3.articles__slider-title Elements that may be missed when designing the UI
              p.articles__slider-desc This is an article that talks about the little elements that are often overlooked when designing UI.
